OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776636668
OL,3,COfficial biographer of Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII is named
OL,6,FThe official biographer of the late
OL,7,FQueen Elizabeth II has been named.
OL,9,FHistorian Dr Anna Keay, whose most
OL,10,Fcelebrated book is about Britain's
OL,11,Frepublican period, has been confirmed
OL,12,Fas taking on the role.
OL,14,FThe title will allow Dr Keay to be
OL,15,Fable to talk with members of the royal
OL,16,Ffamily, along with the late Queen's
OL,17,Ffriends and household as part of her
OL,18,Fresearch for the book. She will also
OL,19,Fhave access to the Queen's personal
OL,20,Fand official papers held in the Royal
OL,21,FArchives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
