OL,3,COfficial biographer of Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII is named
OL,6,FIt has been broadly reported that King
OL,7,FCharles wanted a female author for the
OL,8,Ftask, and that the academic was in
OL,9,Ftalks for the presitigious role.
OL,11,FOfficial royal biographies sometimes
OL,12,Fthrow up unexpected facts or details
OL,13,Fabout the subject's life and shed
OL,14,Flight on important periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
