OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776636668
OL,3,COfficial biographer of Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII is named
OL,6,FDr Keay is a trustee of the Royal
OL,7,FCollection Trust, which the King
OL,8,Fsupports as patron, and is a member of
OL,9,Fthe Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee.
OL,11,FShe has written a number of books
OL,12,Fabout British history and culture
OL,13,Fincluding The Restless Republic:
OL,14,FBritain Without A Crown, which
OL,15,Fchronicles the 11 years Britain was a
OL,16,Frepublic after Charles I was tried and
OL,17,Fexecuted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
