OL,3,COfficial biographer of Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII is named
OL,6,FHer other titles include 'The Crown
OL,7,FJewels: The official illustrated
OL,8,Fhistory', and 'Landmark: A History of
OL,9,FBritain in 50 Buildings'.
OL,11,FThe historian added: "I am deeply
OL,12,Fgrateful to His Majesty the King for
OL,13,Fentrusting me with this responsibility
OL,14,Fand for granting me access to her
OL,15,Fpapers, and will do all I can to do
OL,16,Fjustice to her life and work."
